Require list:

1. cmake ( sudo apt-get install cmake )
2. FLAC - libflac++-dev
3. PAI - lua ( sudo apt-get install liblua5.1-0-dev )
4. ImageMagic - 

To use project in Eclipse:

cmake -G"Eclipse CDT4 - Unix Makefiles" -DECLIPSE_CDT4_GENERATE_SOURCE_PROJECT=TRUE .




### for developers
sudo ln -s ~/workspace/SilentMedia/src /usr/include/libsml



$ cmake .
$ make 
or
$ make VERBOSE=1

$ make clean

